Photos.Model

Class Photo

  • java.lang.Object
    • Photos.Model.Photo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Photo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Defines a Photo for the library, which has a caption, date, directory, and a hashmap of tags. This class is serializable.
    Author:
    Krysti Leong, April Dizon
